      <h3>Mobile Metrics</h3>
      <p>Mobile Metrics automates existing paper data collection processes to easily graph trends in real-time. Log sheets can take days or even months to compile and trend. With Mobile Metrics, you can now create log sheets that can be shared with employees. Create log sheets with Streamlyne's web application, and it automtically pushes it to Streamlyne's mobile web application to use in the field collecting data. This allows you to digitally capture non-DCS data which can be used to build Sceanrios, or tojust simply track in real-time.
