    <h3>Hydrates</h3>
    <p>Hydrates can be insidious to any plant, and can be difficult to track. Hydrates are common but some are extremely lethal if left to form. Streamlyne allows you to input any string of “triggers” (sensors) for any hydrate scenario to help you identify when a hydrate is forming. You can now easily track the progress of a hydrate event by inputting sensor high and low thresholds to assist in your diagnosis.
